channel.title: My VERY Problem
channel.description:
Hey, this I posted at http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,413135.0/all.html And now I'm posting it here because no one reads it there.. If a mod or a nice guy (hopefully will be mod after helping me out) can help me, check out the thread at the URL and answer my questions and help me out. ;)
Well, this is my VERY problem. Listening on port 43594. NOOOOOTHING HAPPENING! If SOMEONE could EVER help me... Then I will cry, so geek am I. I pray for GOD, dudes! I just do SO MUCH want to host a fully working server that I can edit! I will share everything with me if you want! I will invite my whole school and everything! If you want me to take screenshots or anything else, I will really. I do anything for this!! I will help you people to help me! I am using Windows XP. Please give feedback or whatever it's called! Maybe I forgot that you connect whit Moparscape client? Well, if so, I still wonder why it just says that error.. Listening on port 43594. I'm still trying to solve this problem myself to 110% but I don't really suceed, I'm active nerd. Or do I need the client you posted under the source? Or is it your server? Well, if so I will check that out too. I will give you reputation so much you ever may take to the first person who helps me out whit this. [Day 1] Trying to connect from the client u posted.. I also followed the tut about how to change IP. I aslo discovered u may change the port. Any ways it says error_js5connect or something like that and I think it's about the port? What u guys recomend? portforwarding through router (I can't connect to the router, don't know how to find out really much information needed about it)? Or µtorrent or similiar? Then howto? Also: If I connect through that Jagex client.. Then how do I edit source and such? Maybe you just think I'm newbie but I really need help, I will be greatful or however it's spelled.. [Day 2] Trying to download some portforwarder program, today our network crashed, now I'm using someone else network. We will get help from Telia, our rooter is their product, I think.. //Lolle ________________________ Love is my name IRL!!!! <3<3<3333 OMG! you may also email me at [mr.lolle@live.se]
